<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hey, <%= @assignee.firstname %></h1>
    <p>
      I've noticed that you have some issues in your queue that haven't been updated in at least <%= @days.to_s %> days
	  
	  Just to remind you the following issues may need attention
	  <ol>
	  	<% @issues.each do | issue | %>
		 <li><a href="<%=@base_url.to_s + issue.id.to_s %>"><%=issue.subject.to_s %></a></li> 
		<% end %>
	 </ol> 
    </p>
     
  </body>
</html>

